doc.after: In addition to the House Master, each house has a House Captain and a House Captain of Games. Some Houses choose to select more than one. House prefects were once elected from the oldest year, but this no longer happens. The old term, Library, survives in the name of the room set aside for the oldest year's use, where boys have their own kitchen. The situation is similar with the boys in their penultimate year, who have a similar room known as Debate.
